sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Customer as Customer (Cell Phone)
    participant PSTN as Telecom Carrier (PSTN)
    participant CCaaS as CCaaS Platform (AWS/Genesys)
    participant DB as Backend CRM / Database
    actor Agent as Agent (Web Browser)

    Customer->>PSTN: Dials 1-800-555-0199
    PSTN->>CCaaS: SIP INVITE (Incoming Call over Internet)
    CCaaS-->>PSTN: 100 Trying / 200 OK (Call Established)
    
    activate CCaaS
    CCaaS->>Customer: Plays "Welcome to our Support Center"
    CCaaS->>Customer: Plays "Please enter your Account Number"
    Customer->>CCaaS: Keys in "12345" (DTMF Tones)
    
    CCaaS->>DB: API Data Dip (Get user by Account 12345)
    DB-->>CCaaS: Returns Customer Profile (VIP Status: True)
    
    Note right of CCaaS: Routing Decision:<br/>Push to High Priority Queue
    
    CCaaS->>Agent: Rings WebRTC Softphone
    CCaaS->>Agent: Triggers CRM "Screen Pop" with Profile
    Agent-->>CCaaS: Accepts Call
    
    Note over Customer,Agent: Two-Way Audio Established (RTP)
    deactivate CCaaS
